   Politics &amp; Policy:
   Product-Liability Bill Provides Opportunity
   For Long-Term Milking of PACs by Congress
   ----
   By Jill Abramson
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/21/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A16
</SO>
